text: Holmi or Holmoi () was a town of ancient Phrygia. It is mention by Strabo as lying on the main road from Carura to Lycaonia near that road's entry into the mountainous region. Its site is unlocated. ==References== Category:Populated places in Phrygia Category:Former populated places in Turkey Category:Lost ancient cities and towns
title: Holmi (Phrygia)
